628adcc97f034379d2d28c2639f55fe0aebf7","tid":167672,"uid":46469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最怕有d變態，用呢個app扮領養跟住虐待佢地<br />\n<br />\n要搵方法防止</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗都會有家訪、留低電話資料，<br />\n以便follow狗仔/貓仔嘅近況依d basic嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a9535cd0a8230fe025c50b66c17619d228f41c","tid":167672,"uid":46469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登巴絲整既好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n光宗耀祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b9b81369af1943506b51351a06dd9153f46e41","tid":167672,"uid":2752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最怕有d變態，用呢個app扮領養跟住虐待佢地<br />\n<br />\n要搵方法防止</blockquote><br />\n有紀錄有聯絡資料？<br />\n不過佢有心玩野，領養個陣扮無野都吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d2a256b1401d3e013fae6cbdd33416eb3ebb18","tid":167672,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"Ho ball 但係睇錯it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9307cf00b2d78f09433449b494eeec777303f62f","tid":167672,"uid":3196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bbde2d7d75f10d442114ec6f640af7e8a45547c","tid":167672,"uid":3196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ho ball 但係睇錯it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係IT狗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce6a2b8cba6fbf70255df4a9e7f3ae34e0cc637","tid":167672,"uid